---
const { compact = false } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="card" aria-labelledby="support">
  <h2 id="support" style="margin-top:0;">Support the Reavers</h2>
  <p>Love what we do and want to help us outfit new fighters book venues and grow a youth program Your support keeps steel on the list and smiles in the team</p>
  <p style="margin:0 0 12px;">If you are able chip in any amount here</p>
  <p style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <a class="btn" href="https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=REPLACE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Donate via PayPal</a>
    <a class="btn alt" href="https://ko-fi.com/REPLACE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buy us a coffee</a>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin:0;">
    Every bit helps and is never expected If donating is not an option please share our socials and come swing a sword with us
  </p>
</section>
